Hi! I am Greenhornet553.

The name is weird, I know, I've only kept it because I've been using it for a few years now and I seem to forget other usernames that I use.

So hello, I have introduced myself.

Hello Greenhornet553, and welcome to the forum!

There are any number of weird names to be found here, along with a very interesting and engaging community.

Happy landings!

Hello, Greenhornet553!

I use variants of this name as much as I can, so don't worry. Welcome aboard!
Just landed in the forum myself.  Happy to have you.
